Author: grossenten98
Text: I have no idea but I can relate, my friend had invited me to eat at a Mexican restaurant with her and I had a Quesadilla. I ate half of it and the rest for breakfast but I was like freaking out about the Cheese density. Like ermagehrd but it was delicious. But try not to stress over it, it’s therapeutic eating mystery foods ever so often. Well, good job, I commend thou art‘s boldness for going to a restaurant with zilch cal info!
